question: I am a 46 year old female.  I am of average height and weight.  Over the last several months have noticed a change in my urine.  It feel as if it's thick and has a strong sweet smell to it.  Nothing about my diet or lifestyle has changed.  It has me concerned because there is a history of diabetes (stage 2) that runs in my family.  Should I be concerned.
title: Strong Urine Smell
